{"word":"G1301 - διατηρέω - diatēréō - dee-at-ay-reh'-o - Keep","sections":[{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">διατηρέω</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong><span class=\"transliteration\">diatēréō</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong><span class=\"phonetic\">dee-at-ay-reh'-o</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong><span class=\"short-definition\">Keep</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>இலக்கண சொல்வகை / Part(s) of speech: </strong>Verb / வினைச்சொல்</span>"},{"paragraph":"வினைச்சொல் - வைத்துக்கொள், காத்துக்கொள்"},{"paragraph":"to keep continually or carefully"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English: </strong>From <a href=\"#/G1223 - διά - diá - dee-ah'/1223\">G1223</a> and <a href=\"#/G5083 - τηρέω - tēréō - tay-reh'-o/5083\">G5083</a>; to <i>watch thoroughly</i>, that is, (positively and transitively) to <i>observe</i> strictly, or (negatively and reflexively) to <i>avoid</i> wholly: - keep.</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>தொடர்புடைய எண்கள் / Cognate: </strong><a href=\"#/G1301/1301\">G1301</a>, <a href=\"#/G3906/3906\">G3906</a>, <a href=\"#/G3907/3907\">G3907</a>, <a href=\"#/G4933/4933\">G4933</a>, <a href=\"#/G5083/5083\">G5083</a>, <a href=\"#/G5084/5084\">G5084</a>"}]}